    v2 = (0.48 - ((tmp + 0.76 + tmp + 0.77) - (tmp + 0.44 - v0 + 0.76)))
    v2 = wp.exp((v0 - (v0 + 0.87 * tmp + 0.98)))
    v1 = 0.41
